name: UAnimBoneCompressionSettings
doc:
* This object is used to wrap a bone compression codec. It allows a clean integration in the editor by avoiding the need
* to create asset types and factory wrappers for every codec.

Codecs: A list of animation bone compression codecs to try. Empty entries are ignored but the array cannot be empty.
ErrorThreshold: When compressing, the best codec below this error threshold will be used.
bForceBelowThreshold: Any codec (even one that increases the size) with a lower error will be used until it falls below the threshold.
